       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. CURRENCY-ROUND.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-AMOUNT        PIC 9(5)V99 VALUE 12345.67.
       01  WS-RATE          PIC 9V999   VALUE 1.075.
       01  WS-RESULT        PIC 9(6)V99.
       01  WS-DISPLAY       PIC Z(5)9.99.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
           COMPUTE WS-RESULT ROUNDED = WS-AMOUNT * WS-RATE.
           MOVE WS-RESULT TO WS-DISPLAY.
           DISPLAY "AMOUNT: 12345.67".
           DISPLAY "RATE: 1.075".
           DISPLAY "RESULT: " WS-DISPLAY.
           STOP RUN.
